```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Trigger as Event Trigger
    participant API as Django API
    participant Readiness as readiness.py
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FE as React Frontend
    actor User

    Note over Trigger,User: Readiness recalculation — triggered by multiple events

    Note over Trigger: Trigger events:
    Note over Trigger: - ChecklistItem status changed
    Note over Trigger: - ClientDocument status changed (approved/rejected)
    Note over Trigger: - ExtractedIncome/Expense approved
    Note over Trigger: - AccountantAction resolved
    Note over Trigger: - Manual accountant recalculate click

    Trigger->>API: Event occurs (e.g. document approved)
    API->>Readiness: recalculate_readiness(engagement_id)

    Readiness->>DB: SELECT engagement WITH checklist_items, documents, extractions, actions
    DB-->>Readiness: engagement state snapshot

    Note over Readiness: Dimension 1: Documents (weight 40%)
    Readiness->>Readiness: mandatory_docs = [d for d in checklist if d.required]
    Readiness->>Readiness: approved_mandatory = [d for d in mandatory_docs if d.status == 'approved']
    Readiness->>Readiness: doc_score = (approved_mandatory / mandatory_docs) * 100

    Note over Readiness: Dimension 2: Checklist (weight 30%)
    Readiness->>Readiness: total_items = count(checklist_items)
    Readiness->>Readiness: done_items = count(items WHERE status IN [accepted, waived])
    Readiness->>Readiness: checklist_score = (done_items / total_items) * 100

    Note over Readiness: Dimension 3: Verification (weight 20%)
    Readiness->>Readiness: verified = count(extractions WHERE review_status = 'approved')
    Readiness->>Readiness: total = count(extractions)
    Readiness->>Readiness: verification_score = (verified / total) * 100 if total > 0 else 100

    Note over Readiness: Dimension 4: Accountant Review (weight 10%)
    Readiness->>Readiness: open_actions = count(AccountantActions WHERE status = 'open')
    Readiness->>Readiness: review_score = 100 if open_actions == 0 else max(0, 100 - open_actions * 20)

    Note over Readiness: Weighted score
    Readiness->>Readiness: raw_score = (doc*0.4 + checklist*0.3 + verification*0.2 + review*0.1)

    Note over Readiness: Mandatory evidence gating
    alt Any mandatory document missing (status not in [approved, rejected+replaced])
        Readiness->>Readiness: score = min(raw_score, 80)
        Readiness->>Readiness: gate_reason = "Mandatory document missing"
    else All mandatory docs present
        Readiness->>Readiness: score = raw_score
        Readiness->>Readiness: gate_reason = null
    end

    Note over Readiness: Ready-to-file gate
    alt score >= 85 AND missing_items == 0 AND needs_review_docs == 0
        Readiness->>Readiness: ready_to_file = True
    else
        Readiness->>Readiness: ready_to_file = False
    end

    Readiness->>Readiness: explanation = build_explanation(dimensions, gate_reason, score)
    Readiness-->>API: {score, ready_to_file, explanation, dimensions}

    API->>DB: UPDATE TaxEngagement SET readiness_score=score, ready_to_file=ready_to_file
    API->>DB: INSERT ReadinessSnapshot (score, dimensions, explanation, timestamp)
    API->>DB: INSERT PortalAuditLog (action=readiness_updated, score_before, score_after)

    Note over API,FE: Real-time update (polling every 10-20s)
    FE->>API: GET /api/portal/client/ (polling interval)
    API-->>FE: {readiness_score: 82, ready_to_file: false, explanation: "..."}
    FE-->>User: Readiness ring animates from 72 → 82
    FE-->>User: "Your checklist is 82% complete. Missing: jaaropgaaf 2024."
```
